---
---

<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="features-inner">

    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <h2 class="section-title">Everything you need,<br /><em>nothing you don't.</em></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">A self-hosted finance tracker built for people who want clarity without complexity.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid reveal-stagger">

      <!-- ⌘K Command bar — wide -->
      <div class="card card--wide reveal">
        <div class="card-text">
          <span class="tag">AI-powered</span>
          <h3>⌘K to log anything</h3>
          <p>Open the command bar and type naturally — "sushi 28 dinner with Sarah" — or navigate the app. Zeni's AI extracts the amount, category, date, and tags automatically.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Natural language parsing</li>
            <li>Auto-creates new categories</li>
            <li>Suggests relevant tags</li>
            <li>Review &amp; edit before saving</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-demo">
          <div class="demo-input">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--forest)" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
            <span>sushi 28 dinner with Sarah</span>
          </div>
          <div class="demo-fields">
            <div class="demo-field"><span class="demo-label">Amount</span><strong>$28.00</strong></div>
            <div class="demo-field"><span class="demo-label">Category</span><strong>🍣 Dining</strong></div>
            <div class="demo-field">
              <span class="demo-label">Tags</span>
              <span class="chip">dinner</span>
              <span class="chip chip--new">✦ sarah</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Voice -->
      <div class="card reveal">
        <div class="icon-wrap" style="background: oklch(92% 0.04 20);">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="oklch(52% 0.14 20)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/>
            <path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="23"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="23" x2="16" y2="23"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Voice input</h3>
        <p>Tap the mic and speak your expense. Whisper transcribes it locally or via an external provider — your choice, your data.</p>
        <span class="detail">Local Whisper · External STT · No audio leaves your server</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Receipt scanning -->
      <div class="card reveal">
        <div class="icon-wrap" style="background: oklch(92% 0.06 230);">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="oklch(42% 0.1 230)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
            <path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Receipt scanning</h3>
        <p>Paste or attach a photo of any receipt. The AI reads the total, merchant, and date — no manual entry needed.</p>
        <span class="detail">Paste from clipboard · Attach file · Instant parse</span>
      </div>

      <!-- AI Chat -->
      <div class="card reveal" id="ai">
        <div class="icon-wrap" style="background: oklch(92% 0.04 230);">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="oklch(42% 0.1 230)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Chat with your data</h3>
        <p>Ask anything in plain language. "How much did I spend on food last month?" — Zeni answers with your actual numbers.</p>
        <div class="chat-bubbles">
          <div class="bubble bubble--user">Any tips on where I could cut back?</div>
          <div class="bubble bubble--ai">Your dining spend is 34% above last month. Cooking at home 2–3 more times per week could save ~$120.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Budgets -->
      <div class="card reveal">
        <div class="icon-wrap" style="background: oklch(92% 0.06 65);">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="oklch(42% 0.14 65)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Smart budgets</h3>
        <p>Set weekly or monthly limits per category. Get warned at 80% and alerted when exceeded — right on the dashboard.</p>
        <div class="budget-bars">
          <div class="brow">
            <span>Dining</span>
            <div class="btrack"><div class="bfill bfill--animate" data-width="82" style="background: var(--amber);"></div></div>
            <span class="bpct" style="color: var(--amber);">82%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="brow">
            <span>Transport</span>
            <div class="btrack"><div class="bfill bfill--animate" data-width="45" style="background: var(--forest);"></div></div>
            <span class="bpct" style="color: var(--forest-light);">45%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="brow">
            <span>Shopping</span>
            <div class="btrack"><div class="bfill bfill--animate" data-width="100" style="background: var(--rose);"></div></div>
            <span class="bpct" style="color: var(--rose);">112%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Recurring -->
      <div class="card reveal">
        <div class="icon-wrap" style="background: oklch(92% 0.04 155);">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="oklch(38% 0.09 155)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="23 4 23 10 17 10"/>
            <polyline points="1 20 1 14 7 14"/>
            <path d="M3.51 9a9 9 0 0 1 14.85-3.36L23 10M1 14l4.64 4.36A9 9 0 0 0 20.49 15"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Recurring expenses</h3>
        <p>Track subscriptions and regular bills. Set daily, weekly, biweekly, monthly, or yearly schedules — Zeni reminds you when they're due.</p>
        <span class="detail">Netflix · Rent · Gym · Insurance</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Multi-wallet -->
      <div class="card reveal">
        <div class="icon-wrap" style="background: oklch(92% 0.04 80);">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="oklch(35% 0.02 80)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M20 12V22H4V12"/>
            <path d="M22 7H2v5h20V7z"/>
            <path d="M12 22V7"/>
            <path d="M12 7H7.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5C11 2 12 7 12 7z"/>
            <path d="M12 7h4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5C13 2 12 7 12 7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Multiple wallets</h3>
        <p>Separate personal, business, and shared expenses across wallets. Each wallet has its own currency, history, and analytics.</p>
        <span class="detail">Multi-currency · Per-wallet analytics</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Categories & Tags -->
      <div class="card reveal">
        <div class="icon-wrap" style="background: oklch(92% 0.06 280);">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="oklch(42% 0.1 280)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M20.59 13.41l-7.17 7.17a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0L2 12V2h10l8.59 8.59a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.82z"/>
            <line x1="7" y1="7" x2="7.01" y2="7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Categories &amp; tags</h3>
        <p>Organise with emoji-icon categories and freeform tags. The AI suggests both automatically — you can always override.</p>
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag-pill" style="background: oklch(92% 0.06 155); color: oklch(32% 0.08 155);">🍽 Dining</span>
          <span class="tag-pill" style="background: oklch(92% 0.06 230); color: oklch(32% 0.08 230);">✈️ Travel</span>
          <span class="tag-pill" style="background: oklch(92% 0.06 65); color: oklch(42% 0.1 65);">🛒 Groceries</span>
          <span class="tag-pill" style="background: oklch(92% 0.04 80); color: oklch(35% 0.02 80);">#work</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Dashboard — wide, flipped -->
      <div class="card card--wide card--flip reveal">
        <div class="dashboard-preview">
          <div class="dp-cards">
            <div class="dp-card" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--forest);">
              <span class="dp-label">This month</span>
              <span class="dp-value">$1,240</span>
              <span class="dp-sub">42 expenses</span>
            </div>
            <div class="dp-card" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--amber);">
              <span class="dp-label">This week</span>
              <span class="dp-value">$318</span>
              <span class="dp-sub">11 expenses</span>
            </div>
            <div class="dp-card" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--sky);">
              <span class="dp-label">Daily avg</span>
              <span class="dp-value">$41</span>
              <span class="dp-sub">this month</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dp-chart">
            <svg class="donut-svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="88" height="88">
              <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="36" fill="none" stroke="var(--cream-darker)" stroke-width="14"/>
              <circle class="donut-seg donut-seg--1" cx="50" cy="50" r="36" fill="none" stroke="var(--forest)" stroke-width="14"
                stroke-dasharray="84 226" stroke-dashoffset="0" transform="rotate(-90 50 50)"/>
              <circle class="donut-seg donut-seg--2" cx="50" cy="50" r="36" fill="none" stroke="var(--amber)" stroke-width="14"
                stroke-dasharray="43 226" stroke-dashoffset="-84" transform="rotate(-90 50 50)"/>
              <circle class="donut-seg donut-seg--3" cx="50" cy="50" r="36" fill="none" stroke="var(--sky)" stroke-width="14"
                stroke-dasharray="16 226" stroke-dashoffset="-127" transform="rotate(-90 50 50)"/>
            </svg>
            <div class="dp-legend">
              <div class="dp-row"><span class="dp-dot" style="background:var(--forest)"></span><span>Dining</span><strong>$496</strong></div>
              <div class="dp-row"><span class="dp-dot" style="background:var(--amber)"></span><span>Transport</span><strong>$248</strong></div>
              <div class="dp-row"><span class="dp-dot" style="background:var(--sky)"></span><span>Shopping</span><strong>$89</strong></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <span class="tag">Analytics</span>
          <h3>Dashboard at a glance</h3>
          <p>Monthly total, weekly pace, daily average, budget status, recent transactions, and a category breakdown chart — all loading instantly on open.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  const prefersReduced = window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches;

  const cardObserver = new IntersectionObserver(
    (entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (!entry.isIntersecting) return;

        const el = entry.target;

        const bars = el.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.bfill--animate');
        bars.forEach((bar) => {
          const w = bar.dataset.width ?? '0';
          if (prefersReduced) {
            bar.style.width = `${w}%`;
          } else {
            bar.style.width = '0%';
            requestAnimationFrame(() => {
              bar.style.transition = 'width 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)';
              bar.style.width = `${Math.min(Number(w), 100)}%`;
            });
          }
        });

        const donut = el.querySelector('.donut-svg');
        if (donut) {
          const segs = donut.querySelectorAll<SVGCircleElement>('.donut-seg');
          if (prefersReduced) return;
          segs.forEach((seg, i) => {
            const finalDash = seg.getAttribute('stroke-dasharray') ?? '0 226';
            const finalOffset = seg.getAttribute('stroke-dashoffset') ?? '0';
            seg.setAttribute('stroke-dasharray', `0 226`);
            seg.style.transition = `stroke-dasharray 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) ${i * 120 + 100}ms, stroke-dashoffset 0s`;
            requestAnimationFrame(() => {
              seg.setAttribute('stroke-dasharray', finalDash);
              seg.setAttribute('stroke-dashoffset', finalOffset);
            });
          });
        }

        cardObserver.unobserve(el);
      });
    },
    { threshold: 0.3 }
  );

  document.querySelectorAll('.card').forEach((card) => cardObserver.observe(card));
</script>

<style>
.features {
  padding: clamp(64px, 8vw, 100px) 0;
}

.features-inner {
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 clamp(20px, 5vw, 48px);
}

.section-header {
  margin-bottom: clamp(40px, 6vw, 64px);
  max-width: 560px;
}

.section-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.1;
  color: var(--ink);
}
.section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--forest-light); }

.section-sub {
  font-size: clamp(14px, 1.5vw, 16px);
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin-top: 14px;
}

/* ── Grid ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 16px;
}

/* ── Cards ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.card {
  background: white;
  border: 1px solid var(--cream-darker);
  border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 28px);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
  transition:
    transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1),
    box-shadow 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1),
    border-color 0.3s;
}

.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  border-color: var(--sand);
}

.card--wide {
  grid-column: span 2;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 24px;
  align-items: center;
}

.card--flip {
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
}

.card--flip .dashboard-preview { order: 1; }
.card--flip .card-text { order: 2; }

.card h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 22px);
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.card p {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  line-height: 1.65;
}

.tag {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-light);
  background: var(--cream-dark);
  border: 1px solid var(--cream-darker);
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border-radius: 100px;
  width: fit-content;
}

.detail {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  margin-top: auto;
}

.icon-wrap {
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  transition: transform 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1);
}

.card:hover .icon-wrap {
  transform: scale(1.08);
}

.card-text {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10px;
}

.card ul {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 6px;
}

.card ul li {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  padding-left: 16px;
  position: relative;
}

.card ul li::before {
  content: '–';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
}

/* ── Command bar demo ───────────────────────────────────── */
.card-demo {
  background: var(--cream);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--cream-darker);
}

.demo-input {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 12px 14px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-darker);
  background: white;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--ink);
}

.demo-fields {
  padding: 10px 12px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 6px;
}

.demo-field {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

.demo-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  width: 64px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.demo-field strong {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--ink);
}

.chip {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  background: white;
  border: 1px solid var(--cream-darker);
  padding: 2px 7px;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

.chip--new {
  color: oklch(38% 0.09 145);
  background: oklch(92% 0.04 145);
  border-color: oklch(82% 0.08 145);
}

/* ── Chat bubbles ───────────────────────────────────────── */
.chat-bubbles {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-top: 4px;
}

.bubble {
  font-size: 13px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  padding: 9px 12px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  max-width: 90%;
}

.bubble--user {
  background: var(--forest);
  color: var(--cream);
  align-self: flex-end;
  border-radius: 12px 3px 12px 12px;
}

.bubble--ai {
  background: var(--cream-dark);
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  align-self: flex-start;
  border-radius: 3px 12px 12px 12px;
}

/* ── Budget bars ────────────────────────────────────────── */
.budget-bars {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-top: 4px;
}

.brow {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
}

.brow span:first-child { width: 72px; flex-shrink: 0; }

.btrack {
  flex: 1;
  height: 5px;
  background: var(--cream-dark);
  border-radius: 99px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.bfill {
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 99px;
  width: 0%;
}

.bpct {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  width: 36px;
  text-align: right;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* ── Tag pills ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
.tag-row {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 6px;
  margin-top: 4px;
}

.tag-pill {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border-radius: 100px;
  transition: transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1);
}

.tag-pill:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }

/* ── Dashboard preview ──────────────────────────────────── */
.dashboard-preview {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
}

.dp-cards {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
}

.dp-card {
  background: white;
  border: 1px solid var(--cream-darker);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 10px 14px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2px;
}

.dp-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
}

.dp-value {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 20px;
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: 1.1;
}

.dp-sub {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
}

.dp-chart {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  background: white;
  border: 1px solid var(--cream-darker);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 12px 14px;
}

.dp-legend {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 6px;
  flex: 1;
}

.dp-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 7px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
}

.dp-row span:nth-child(2) { flex: 1; }
.dp-row strong { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink); }

.dp-dot {
  width: 7px;
  height: 7px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* ── Donut chart ────────────────────────────────────────── */
.donut-seg {
  transition: stroke-dasharray 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}

/* ── Responsive ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }

  .card--wide {
    grid-column: span 2;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .card--flip {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .card--wide {
    grid-column: span 1;
  }
}
</style>
